22 (3) "Cosmetologist" means a person who engages in the practice of cosmetology for the
23 public generally or for consideration, regardless of the name under which the
24 practice is conducted;
25 (4) "Cosmetology" means the practice of:
26 (a) Hair styling;
27 (b) Esthetics; and
